result.name: Cafe Merry Go Round 過客

reviews.text: Quite a chill place. Love how they position the seats around the place, the sofa as well as the decorations are nice and chic. The environment is neat too. The food items are okay, the pasta is in better value. Quality of finger foods is better than we expected. Lots of choices for drinks. Good value!
Sunday flea market! Wonderful place on the rooftop,great wares. The fish and chips are amazing...
Fantastic place to sit outside and enjoy a drink without any noise in the middle of Causeway Bay. Very welcoming staff too.
A relaxing place, with affordable price range for a drink.  Dun be misunderstanding root floor equal to a  luxury price, this place will exceed your expectation.
Chilllllllllll~

reviews.text: Lovely building, we had some lovely Korean food in one of the restaurants there. It took a while to find it from the local train station, but it's worth the adventure. Staff are friendly enough within the building. I would definitely go again if I'm ever in Hong Kong.

This is a brand new plaza, containing a lot of restaurants, including Korean food, Vietnamese food, and the very heat China brand for hot pot on the ground food.  And every restaurants are very good and should try all of them.
New building with some signature restaurants, worth to have a try....
